Class Volvo240

java.lang.Object
DoublePoint

Volvo240
All Implemented Interfaces:

public class Volvo240
extends Vehicle
This class creates a Saab95 object/car. It inherits the Vehicle class that contains common values needed.

    • speedFactor

      public double speedFactor()
      This methods calculates the speedfactor of the car using trimFactor

    • incrementSpeed

      public void incrementSpeed​(double amount)
      This method increases the speed of the car with the minimum of current speed with an extra speed depending on @code amount}, or the enginePower. currentSpeed can never be outside of the interval [0,enginePower] so acceptableInterval is used in method.

    • decrementSpeed

      public void decrementSpeed​(double amount)
      This method decreases the speed of the car with the maximum of current speed subtracted by an amount depending on amount, or enginePower. currentSpeed can never be outside of the interval [0,enginePower] so acceptableInterval is used in method.

    • gas

      public void gas​(double amount)

      public void brake​(double amount)
